<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />In the day of my trouble I sought the Lord;</para>

<para style="q1">at night I stretched my hands out, and they would not become tired.</para>

<para style="q1">My soul refused to be comforted.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />I thought of God as I groaned;</para>

<para style="q1">I thought about him as I grew faint.

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>

